title: Let Free the Curse of Taekwondo
overview: Juyoung reunites with his long-lost first love, Dohoi, whom he has been desperately searching for, at a funeral after twelve years. "It feels like everything is cursedâ€¦" Twelve years ago, the two of them shared a tender love, empathizing with each other's wounds. How did they end up estranged from each other? Dohoi, who found his own dream instead of Taekwondo as he desired, and Juyoung, who still does Taekwondo, can break the curse of the past now, twelve years later?
